[22:15] <luqui> for example:

[22:15] <luqui> (in haskell, but I'll keep it simple)

[22:15] <luqui> [ x + y | x <- [1..10], y <- [1..10], x > y ]

[22:16] <luqui> [3,4,5,5,6,7,6,7,8,...

